@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Lọc Audit Log
autonumber

actor "Quản trị viên" as Admin
boundary "audit_logs.html" as UI
control "AuditAdminController" as Ctrl
participant "AuditService" as Svc
participant "AuditLogRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> UI: Chọn ngày lọc
UI -> Ctrl: GET /admin/api/audit-logs/content?date=...&page=...
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Svc: searchLogsByDate(date,page,size)
activate Svc

Svc -> Svc: Parse date -> startDate/endDate

Svc -> Repo: searchLogs(startDate,endDate,pageable)
activate Repo

Repo -> DB: SELECT audit_logs theo ngày
activate DB
DB --> Repo: Page<AuditLog>
deactivate DB

Repo --> Svc: Page<AuditLog>
deactivate Repo

Svc --> Ctrl: Page<AuditLog>
deactivate Svc

Ctrl --> UI: Render fragment content
deactivate Ctrl

UI --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách đã lọc

@enduml